Who We Are 


Your team. You and your family come first.
Balasa Dinverno Foltz LLC (BDF) is an independent private wealth management firm. We manage approximately $3 billion in assets for business owners, women, individuals and families, and institutions.
Objective
As independent advisors, we put you first, always. We provide personalized, objective advice to build and maintain a secure foundation of wealth for your family. Motivated by trust and transparency, we discuss our thinking and decisions with you all along the way. We are vested not only in the well-being of your wealth but also in the well-being of your family.
Team culture
Our unified and personalized approach to wealth management lies in our unique ability to leverage an expansive team of wealth managers and specialized experts to provide our clients with comprehensive solutions. With your goals as our guide and the assistance of a dedicated team of independent experts — Wealth Managers, CPAs, tax specialists, lawyers and insurance professionals, we are able to coordinate the development of an integrated strategy and a realistic road map to help you enjoy a full life.
Conflict free
As a Securities and Exchange Commission Registered Investment Advisor, we are legally responsible to act in your best interest and to avoid (and disclose if present) conflicts of interest. We take this responsibility very seriously.
Recognized
We are proud to be consistently recognized among the industry, including recently being named one of the top local independent advisers by Five Star Professionals as featured in Chicago magazine. (See Important Disclosure Information)
